Definition: agree to plead guilty in return for a lesser charge
Example: If he plea-bargains, he will be sent to a medium-security prison for 8 years
Synonyms: noun, communication, plea_bargain, plea_bargaining, agree, group, law, c, to, plead, guilty, in, return, for, a, lesser, charge, If, he, plea-bargains, will, be, sent, medium-security, prison, years
Frame: 2
Category: verb.communication
